{"tid":1266350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(G20) 巴西總統以行動抗議「習近平」遲到","createTime":"2019-06-29T13:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T16:19:47.000Z","uid":134071,"like":519,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"a375df93dbbb33035f65e6d5f83f4f865f1be2e0","tid":1266350,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"Jair Bolsonaro是現任巴西總統. 被外界稱為「巴西特朗普」<br />\n<br />\nJair Bolsonaro原本已約習近平會面, 但習近平遲到20分鐘.&nbsp; Jair Bolsonaro因此決定取消會面, 官方理由係要趕住搭飛機.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DLBiller/status/1144947598421372928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDLBiller%2Fstatus%2F1144947598421372928&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=0e88e8fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDLBiller%2Fstatus%2F1144947598421372928&h=1cf50b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DLBiller/status/1144947598421372928</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDavid Biller<br />\n&rlm;@DLBiller<br />\n<br />\nBolsonaro had a bilateral scheduled with China's Xi Jinping, who left him waiting 20 minutes. And Bolsonaro had to check out of his hotel &amp; catch his flight, so he canceled the meeting.<br />\n<br />\n5:35 AM - 29 Jun 2019"},{"pid":"4bafde07cffca525a433cb61c693e1c447d6f9b4","tid":1266350,"uid":134071,"like":315,"dislike":0,"score":315,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"仲強硬過正版特朗普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c63f7f81f512f270489ac9dbf83ae4604b0c1e","tid":1266350,"uid":30476,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"唔撚傾呀"},{"pid":"4c27a7e0e7f56053c0e9cb4550347c2835902368","tid":1266350,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb25259af3dcbd8564192fdc799c3e30963cbeeb","tid":1266350,"ui